name: Hanukiya
description: The first in a series of 8 candles against the eight pedestals of the menorah which was lit with only a small jug of oil and in a great miracle illuminated the temple for 8 days.  And so every day add a candle to the menorah until you reach 8 candles as you see in the picture.  This menorah was lit in a Jewish home on the last day of the holiday, today.
